# Local/Render process map. Two long-running processes — the API and the
# ingestion worker — must BOTH be up; a missing worker silently piles clips up
# as "Queued" (the worker is a separate process, not part of the web server).
#
# Locally, prefer ./dev.sh — it adds an auto-restart loop around the worker
# (honcho/foreman tear everything down when one process exits; the worker is the
# fragile one and must come back on its own). This Procfile documents the two
# processes for honcho users and for the Render worker service.
web: uv run uvicorn app.main:app --port 8000
worker: uv run arq app.worker.WorkerSettings
